room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: Some unique puzzles here. Most puzzles themed very well. If you like opening locks, there are plenty in this room. We failed to escape, but still had fun which is the sign of a good room!

room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: This was the best time I have had in a LONG time! DO THIS. DO THE THING.

room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: It was refreshing to find this place. It's fun and different from anything else on this island. Definitely coming back and trying the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: The experience is well worth the price! It keeps you engaged the full 60 minutes and it's amazing for team-building. We tried once and failed (just 90 more seconds!) and returned the next day to redeem ourselves and claimed our shirt! Perfect souvenir!

room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: Great experience! We did mission Manoa and we can't wait to go back to do the other rooms! So close!

room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: The wife and I had an absolute blast. Loved it. Really, truly, gets you thinking. Staff was wonderful, and even though we lost, we're going to come back in the next few days and do a different room.

room_title: Escape room "Mission Manoa" by Breakout Waikiki in Honolulu
review: Had an absolutely amazing time! Great family fun! The staff was very friendly and made the experience very enjoyable. I would definitely recommend this to anyone!
